{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.017.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les r\u00e9tributions divines<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-18: cf. J\u00e9 31:29, 30. (Job 34:10-23. Ro 2:6-11. \u00c9s 3:10, 11.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel me fut adress\u00e9e, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.17.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 17:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.17.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Pourquoi dites-vous ce proverbe dans le pays d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Les p\u00e8res ont mang\u00e9 des raisins verts, et les dents des enfants en ont \u00e9t\u00e9 agac\u00e9es?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Je suis vivant! Dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, vous n\u2019aurez plus lieu de dire ce proverbe en Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Voici, toutes les \u00e2mes sont \u00e0 moi; l\u2019\u00e2me du fils comme l\u2019\u00e2me du p\u00e8re, l\u2019une et l\u2019autre sont \u00e0 moi; l\u2019\u00e2me qui p\u00e8che, c\u2019est celle qui mourra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>L\u2019homme qui est juste, qui pratique la droiture et la justice,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>qui ne mange pas sur les montagnes et ne l\u00e8ve pas les yeux vers les idoles de la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui ne d\u00e9shonore pas la femme de son prochain et ne s\u2019approche pas d\u2019une femme pendant son impuret\u00e9,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>qui n\u2019opprime personne, qui rend au d\u00e9biteur son gage, qui ne commet point de rapines, qui donne son pain \u00e0 celui qui a faim et couvre d\u2019un v\u00eatement celui qui est nu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>qui ne pr\u00eate pas \u00e0 int\u00e9r\u00eat et ne tire point d\u2019usure, qui d\u00e9tourne sa main de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 et juge selon la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 entre un homme et un autre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>qui suit mes lois et observe mes ordonnances en agissant avec fid\u00e9lit\u00e9, celui-l\u00e0 est juste, il vivra, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>S\u2019il a un fils qui soit violent, qui r\u00e9pande le sang, ou qui commette quelque chose de semblable;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>si ce fils n\u2019imite en rien la conduite de son p\u00e8re, s\u2019il mange sur les montagnes, s\u2019il d\u00e9shonore la femme de son prochain,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>s\u2019il opprime le malheureux et l\u2019indigent, s\u2019il commet des rapines, s\u2019il ne rend pas le gage, s\u2019il l\u00e8ve les yeux vers les idoles et fait des abominations,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>s\u2019il pr\u00eate \u00e0 int\u00e9r\u00eat et tire une usure, ce fils-l\u00e0 vivrait! Il ne vivra pas; il a commis toutes ces abominations; qu\u2019il meure! Que son sang retombe sur lui!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais si un homme a un fils qui voie tous les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s que commet son p\u00e8re, qui les voie et n\u2019agisse pas de la m\u00eame mani\u00e8re;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>si ce fils ne mange pas sur les montagnes et ne l\u00e8ve pas les yeux vers les idoles de la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, s\u2019il ne d\u00e9shonore pas la femme de son prochain,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:16","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>s\u2019il n\u2019opprime personne, s\u2019il ne prend point de gage, s\u2019il ne commet point de rapines, s\u2019il donne son pain \u00e0 celui qui a faim et couvre d\u2019un v\u00eatement celui qui est nu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:17","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>s\u2019il d\u00e9tourne sa main de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9, s\u2019il n\u2019exige ni int\u00e9r\u00eat ni usure, s\u2019il observe mes ordonnances et suit mes lois, celui-l\u00e0 ne mourra pas pour l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 de son p\u00e8re; il vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:18","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>C\u2019est son p\u00e8re, qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 un oppresseur, qui a commis des rapines envers les autres, qui a fait au milieu de son peuple ce qui n\u2019est pas bien, c\u2019est lui qui mourra pour son iniquit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:19","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 19-32: cf. \u00c9z 33:7-20. Os 14.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Vous dites: Pourquoi le fils ne porte-t-il pas l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 de son p\u00e8re? C\u2019est que le fils a agi selon la droiture et la justice, c\u2019est qu\u2019il a observ\u00e9 et mis en pratique toutes mes lois; il vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:20","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>L\u2019\u00e2me qui p\u00e8che, c\u2019est celle qui mourra. Le fils ne portera pas l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 de son p\u00e8re, et le p\u00e8re ne portera pas l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 de son fils. La justice du juste sera sur lui, et la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 du m\u00e9chant sera sur lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:21","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Si le m\u00e9chant revient de tous les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s qu\u2019il a commis, s\u2019il observe toutes mes lois et pratique la droiture et la justice, il vivra, il ne mourra pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:22","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Toutes les transgressions qu\u2019il a commises seront oubli\u00e9es; il vivra, \u00e0 cause de la justice qu\u2019il a pratiqu\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:23","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ce que je d\u00e9sire, est-ce que le m\u00e9chant meure? Dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel. N\u2019est-ce pas qu\u2019il change de conduite et qu\u2019il vive?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:24","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Si le juste se d\u00e9tourne de sa justice et commet l\u2019iniquit\u00e9, s\u2019il imite toutes les abominations du m\u00e9chant, vivra-t-il? Toute sa justice sera oubli\u00e9e, parce qu\u2019il s\u2019est livr\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 et au p\u00e9ch\u00e9; \u00e0 cause de cela, il mourra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:25","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Vous dites: La voie du Seigneur n\u2019est pas droite. \u00c9coutez donc, maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! Est-ce ma voie qui n\u2019est pas droite? Ne sont-ce pas plut\u00f4t vos voies qui ne sont pas droites?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:26","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Si le juste se d\u00e9tourne de sa justice et commet l\u2019iniquit\u00e9, et meurt pour cela, il meurt \u00e0 cause de l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 qu\u2019il a commise.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:27","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Si le m\u00e9chant revient de sa m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 et pratique la droiture et la justice, il fera vivre son \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:28","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>S\u2019il ouvre les yeux et se d\u00e9tourne de toutes les transgressions qu\u2019il a commises, il vivra, il ne mourra pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:29","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>La maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl dit: La voie du Seigneur n\u2019est pas droite. Est-ce ma voie qui n\u2019est pas droite, maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl? Ne sont-ce pas plut\u00f4t vos voies qui ne sont pas droites?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:30","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi je vous jugerai chacun selon ses voies, maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Revenez et d\u00e9tournez-vous de toutes vos transgressions, afin que l\u2019iniquit\u00e9 ne cause pas votre ruine.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:31","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Rejetez loin de vous toutes les transgressions par lesquelles vous avez p\u00e9ch\u00e9; faites-vous un c\u0153ur nouveau et un esprit nouveau. Pourquoi mourriez-vous, maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.32","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.32","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:32","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Car je ne d\u00e9sire pas la mort de celui qui meurt, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Convertissez-vous donc, et vivez.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.19.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc7d68a67.87819473');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc7d68a67.87819473\" height